  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Geisha Clan, Level 4+ <br />You always had a special hobby to train some of the more distant skills from your specialty. You gain the following:</p><ul><li>You can choose one of the forsaken skills from your High Nobility trait. This skill becomes available as a choice for that trait.</li><li>You gain 1 rank of mastery that you can apply to any Geisha skill from the High Nobility trait you are proficient with (including the newly unlocked skill).</li><li><p>Depending on the specialty of Geisha you chose, you gain a +1 modifier to one of the following:</p><ul><li><strong>Dancer:</strong> +1 to Dexterity or Strength</li><li><strong>Strategic:</strong> +1 to Intelligence or Wisdom</li><li><strong>Eloquence:</strong> +1 to Wisdom or Charisma</li></ul></li></ul>",
